{"tid":1091292,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"★ g嬸金曲台之 Chyna + Blue Jeans 藍戰士 (^_^)","createTime":"2019-04-04T04:43:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-06T17:43:51.000Z","uid":44730,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"11ed6dbb2efe2c6b0fb7f60adbe96407a06a1d15","tid":1091292,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-04T04:43:24.000Z","msg":"唐龍﹙Don Ashley﹚，本地鼓手、作曲家、填詞和監製人，有「亞洲鼓王」之稱；他是Ramband、 Chyna的鼓手，也是Chyna樂團的成立者及靈魂人物。<br />\n<br />\n父親是英國，母親是馬來西亞人，在香港成長，作為外籍人士，但一直以港自居，懂流利廣東話及英語。<br />\n<br />\n唐龍在一間有樂隊表演的餐廳認識黃良昇 蘇德華和單立文。83年四人組成Chyna樂隊，推出大碟《There's Rock &amp; Roll in Chyna》。<br />\n<br />\n那時的蘇德華和單立文未留長髮，黃良昇則有鬚。他們三人脫離Chyna後，在87年組成 Blue Jeans 藍戰士。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n1988年Chyna出版了他們最滿意的唱片《灰色都市》，唱片有超過十分鐘的Drum Solo，中文歌詞更找來了林夕，可惜政治題材敏感而遭電台禁播。在現在提起八十年代中後期的本地樂隊熱潮中，Chyna反而較少被提起。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/q6r7vLQRxQA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fq6r7vLQRxQA&d=xTo9lt5%2FMO3GrXFnFHQdvLJtyMJyNHaGyUrVEdcKl1A%3D&h=12c2bc08\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/q6r7vLQRxQA</a><br />\n黑太陽<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/LXQ0c0RXacM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FLXQ0c0RXacM&d=xTo9lt5%2FMO3GrXFnFHQdvLJtyMJyNHaGyUrVEdcKl1A%3D&h=98a5d80f\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/LXQ0c0RXacM</a><br />\n灰色都市"},{"pid":"95920e0dd8ed110abdfe8bf55b930b1574c2db24","tid":1091292,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-04T04:43:46.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/w7uzs7WOlz4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fw7uzs7WOlz4&d=xTo9lt5%2FMO3GrXFnFHQdvLJtyMJyNHaGyUrVEdcKl1A%3D&h=10b7ff53\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/w7uzs7WOlz4</a><br />\n<br />\n唐龍與結他王Peter Ng在70年代組成Ramband後在86年重組，用Chyna做隊名，在寶麗金旗下推出EP 《Back 2Gether》，主打是英文歌，亦有廣東歌 《繼續搖擺》。"},{"pid":"52d397cc8832177b52cb95285137fdbd8afcb649","tid":1091292,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-04T04:46:03.000Z","msg":"唐龍在樂壇縱橫多年，曾跟多位本地、台灣歌手合作無間，從溫拿到徐小鳳、張學友、陳奕迅、關淑怡，多次擔任歌曲編曲和演唱會鼓手，並為《我是一隻小小鳥》等大熱金曲擔任編曲。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.donashley.com.hk/halloffame_htm_files/658.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.donashley.com.hk%2Fhalloffame_htm_files%2F658.jpg&h=03635bf0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/WjA3Ko6FXxg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FWjA3Ko6FXxg&d=xTo9lt5%2FMO3GrXFnFHQdvLJtyMJyNHaGyUrVEdcKl1A%3D&h=585680fd\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/WjA3Ko6FXxg</a><br />\n<br />\n唐龍作品：張學友《復活》"},{"pid":"11d0f2ab3b79bb03e49b72e2a1b7acc1ea8d6610","tid":1091292,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-04T05:29:56.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ENY64G4r05Q\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DENY64G4r05Q&d=xTo9lt5%2FMO3GrXFnFHQdvLJtyMJyNHaGyUrVEdcKl1A%3D&h=f2272b3c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ENY64G4r05Q</a><br />\n<br />\nChyna的第一張唱片《There is Rock &amp; Roll In Chyna》，推出後打入美國Billboard排行榜，一首〈Within You&rsquo;ll Remain〉是名曲，被翻唱成六種語言。"},{"pid":"435d265803cae015e0a30dc685d8fbb6ccb50101","tid":1091292,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-04T06:19:20.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/yS2s0wh2UIs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FyS2s0wh2UIs&d=xTo9lt5%2FMO3GrXFnFHQdvLJtyMJyNHaGyUrVEdcKl1A%3D&h=3d72841f\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/yS2s0wh2UIs</a><br />\n<br />\n送上一首 《也許明日再遇上》<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/22/023112_e9fcefa24e589dca0ee88a946b33a1ee.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F22%2F023112_e9fcefa24e589dca0ee88a946b33a1ee.png&h=f99a10a4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7834547a214fbf5498c16a0ffc0720d3d6d485e0","tid":1091292,"uid